exitPositionToVault(address).details: Requires NOT staked. Does NOT harvest gauge rewards implicitly.

harvestGaugeRewardsToBuffer(address).details: This is intentionally NOT called during rebalance flows due to high gas.

harvestPoolFeesToBuffer(address).details: Works even if the position is staked (temporarily withdraws/re-stakes the NFT).

increaseLiquidityFromVault(address,uint2.details: If staked, temporarily withdraw/re-stake the NFT.

unstakePosition(address).details: This does NOT harvest rewards implicitly.

claimRewards(address).notice: Claim rewards to the vault (legacy/manual path).

collectToVault(address).notice: Collect pool fees to vault (idle balances).

currentRange(address).notice: Returns the current tick range and liquidity for a vault position.

currentTokenId(address).notice: Returns the current tokenId for a vault (0 if none).

exitPositionToVaultAndHarvestFeesToBuffe.notice: Exit position to vault while harvesting pool fees to buffer (protocol cut applied).

feeBuffer().notice: Buffer where harvested fees/rewards are credited per vault.

gauge().notice: MasterChefV3 gauge (can be zero if no staking).

harvestGaugeRewardsToBuffer(address).notice: Harvest gauge rewards (e.g., CAKE) into VaultFeeBuffer (protocol cut applied).

harvestPoolFeesToBuffer(address).notice: Harvest pool fees into VaultFeeBuffer (protocol cut applied).

increaseLiquidityFromVault(address,uint2.notice: Increase liquidity using funds pulled from the vault (sourced from buffer withdrawals).

increaseLiquidityWithCaps(address,uint25.notice: Adds idle vault balances into the existing position (no range change).

lastRebalance(address).notice: Optional timestamps (not enforced here; useful for off-chain visibility).

onERC721Received(address,address,uint256.notice: ERC721 receiver hook to accept NFPM token transfers (required for staking integrations).

openInitialPosition(address,int24,int24).notice: Open the initial position using vault balances.

rebalanceWithCaps(address,int24,int24,ui.notice: Rebalance while harvesting outstanding pool fees into VaultFeeBuffer (protocol cut applied).

slot0().notice: Returns sqrtPriceX96 and current tick of the pool.

stakePosition(address).notice: Stake current position in gauge (if configured).

tickSpacing().notice: Returns tick spacing of the underlying pool.

tokens().notice: Returns token0/token1 of the underlying pool.

unstakePosition(address).notice: Unstake current position from gauge (if configured).
